title: Never Ape an Ape Man
description: The gang is hired by Daphne's uncle, a famous director, as extras in his latest project. But the star of the show is a real nasty ape.

title: From Bad to Worse
description: A zombie epidemic strikes in Ooo and it's Princess Bubblegum's fault.

title: Please and Thank You Song
description: Mei goes around the farm with food for the animals. She offers them some food and the animals say "yes please"

title: La Suciedad
description: A Ben le encargan la tarea de limpiar la Chatarra, pero cuando, engañado por los viles villanos Fly Guys, permite que se lo roben, debe perseguirlos antes de que fabriquen una larva monstruosa imparable con un objetivo claro: destruir Las Vegas.

title: Attack of the Weird Al-Osaurus!
description: Driving through the Rocky Mountains, the Mystery Inc. gang discovers a sleep-away accordion camp run by none other than Weird Al Yankovic! But there is no accordion joy when a horrible dinosaur attacks the camp. Can our heroes and Weird Al solve this prehistoric mystery or are they destined to become dino-food?

title: What the Hex Is Going On?
description: When the gang visits the Weatherby estate, they must investigate a mysterious voice and a ghost who demands the family return its fortune to a neighboring clan.

title: Bubble Buddies
description: Steven looks like a hero when he forms a magic crystal bubble around himself to protect a girl he likes from danger, but then panics when he can't figure out how to turn the bubble off!

title: Separacion Rapida
description: Cuando una misteriosa tormenta eléctrica se abate sobre el Omni-Copter en el Ecuador, el equipo Tennyson pronto descubre que Solar y Polar están detrás del suceso.

title: Rainy Day
description: The girls get into trouble when left to entertain themselves on a rainy day.

title: In Dreams
description: Steven's dreams start broadcasting onto his bedroom TV.

title: La Formula de Manzana
description: Manzana necesita encontrar una fórmula divertida que le permita conseguir un papel cómico en una película.

title: The Curse of Elmore
description: When Gumball's schoolfriend Leslie finds an old video tape, the creepy mystery of Elmore's ghostly past unfolds. Featuring spooky and hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: La casa de munecas embrujada
description: Craig y sus amigos descubren que los persigue una muñeca aterradora y su casa de muñecas embrujada.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The Big Trip
description: It's time for the gang's yearly vacation, but Hawk refuses to go, claiming the gang's vacations are never fun for him because the others are terrible at vacationing. Hawk only agrees to go if the gang pass his super-intense vacation training course.

title: The More Things Change Part 2
description: Ben and Rook discover an underground city beneath Bellwood populated with aliens! But who is terrorizing them? (Introducing Nemetrix alien BugLizard, & Ben alien Shocksquatch, Psyphon, Fistina, Bubblehelmet, Liam.)

title: Haunted RV
description: After Uncle Grandpa's Haunted House spirals out of control, the gang must save the teenagers stuck inside.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Scary Tales 2
description: It's Halloween again and the gang is desperately trying to tell the scariest story to a couple of trick or treaters. Each of the characters takes turns adding onto the last story, going through a haunted glove to a haunted action figure to haunted everything, and even a spooky song! None work in scaring the kids when suddenly a full scale alien invasion happens right before their eyes! Still, the trick or treaters are unimpressed until Richard takes the story stage and delivers a story no kid wants to hear- instead of candy, the trick or treaters would get granola bars! The kids, and Puppycorn, run away screaming.

title: Man of the House
description: Clarence's first night home alone spirals out of control, forcing Clarence and his pals to wage war against their own home security measures.

title: Ollie Ollie In-Come Free!
description: When our mystery solving gang agrees to help Ricky Gervais with a haunted antique Egyptian statue of a cat, they find themselves embroiled in a confrontation with the ancient goddess Bast in mummy form!

title: Masters Never Quit
description: Pursued by a magma monster, Cole, Princess Vania, Wu & the Lowly arrive at a mysterious temple deep in Shintaro Mountain, a temple which was once a training ground for Earth Elementals including Cole's own mother, Lilly!

title: The Krakken
description: While stopped at a lakefront campsite, Ben has a chance encounter with a Loch Ness type sea monster called a Krakken, controlled by an evil poacher.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Lars de las estrellas
description: Lars demuestra estar a la altura.

title: Candy Is Dandy/Catastrophe
description: Candy Is Dandy: When the Mayor gives the girls some candy in gratitude for saving the day, they become hooked on the stuff. They even make a deal with a local villain to commit crimes for treats./Catastrophe: A monster is frantically tearing up the town looking for his lost kitty. But in a city the size of Townsville, how can the girls find one lone cat?

title: Mr. Gus Moves Out
description: When a fed-up Mr. Gus moves out of the RV, Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve work together to get him back.

title: Secret Swapper of Doom
description: When the girls get a Paper Fortune Teller that can predict the future if they tell it a secret, they begin to rely on it to predict everything. But when it predicts the Powerpuff Girls will be destroyed, the girls must find a way to stop the future from happening.

title: El gran viaje
description: Es hora de las vacaciones anuales de la banda, pero Halcondrilo se niega a ir, alegando que las vacaciones de la banda nunca son divertidas para él porque los otros son pésimos compañeros de vacaciones. De hecho, Halcondrilo solo acepta ir si la banda aprueba su curso de entrenamiento de vacaciones superintensivo: ilos desafíos temáticos más emocionantes que se puedan imaginar!

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Elmore's Most Wanted
description: Gumball's dad has been revealed as "Elmore's Most Wanted" - but when the Chief of Police tries to investigate, things do not go according to plan. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Have I Got a Deal for You
description: Ben and Rook must stop a giant rampaging alien from destroying Bellwood while dealing with a peace-loving alien-rights activist who doesn't want it hurt. (Introducing Hokestar, Solid Plugg 1st appearance, Pax, Sunder.)

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: Cambia de Parecer
description: Steven se enfrenta al mayor desafío de su vida.

title: Dream Boat
description: Sumo devotes himself to the Sisyphean task of building a boat, defying the expectations of everyone in his life, including himself.

title: Embrujado
description: Robin ignora las reglas de un juego de maleficios y termina perdiendo la voz.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Fiesta Day
description: The Bears party it up with a living piñatas for Fiesta Day. Wanting the festivities to never end, Grizz wishes for it to be Fiesta Day everyday.

title: La Conciencia
description: Gumball y Darwin intentan ser más ecológicos y, como consecuencia, la escuela termina infestada de enredaderas.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Eater
description: It's Halloween and Apple's not feeling quite right. He takes Onion into the dark depths to find out why.

title: The Sunflower
description: Our Trio makes a new friend in the Creek, but when her pet befalls a tragic fate, Kelsey believes she knows how to help.

title: Fool Moon
description: Strange things start happening when Uncle Grandpa installs a moon roof in the RV.

title: Who's the Fake?!/Trouble Busters! 2
description: With the reveal that Haavik is a shapeshifting Alien, the ABs start to get super-paranoid, realizing that ANYONE could be Haavik in disguise. The suspicion quickly turns inward, and the ABs are left wondering if they have an imposter among them!/ A kid brawler named Oliver has lost his Bakugan! This seems like a job for the Trouble Busters. The Awesome Brawlers help him chase down and try to catch the elusive Bakugan, who leads them on a wild goose chase through Los Volmos.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Rise and Shine
description: A glimpse at the wild, secret adventures Clarence undertakes each day before the rest of us, and the sun, get up.

title: El Relopulpo
description: En una pacífica ciudad costera, Ben no solo debe enfrentarse a Vapor Smythe -su arcaico antagonista- y a su última creación, el Relopulpo... isino que también debe enfrentarse a su temor más profundo y oscuro: los calamares!

title: Late Night Talky Time
description: The moon is bored of taking the nightshift, since everyone's always asleep. So Unikitty leads the gang in putting on an over-the-top late night talk show to keep the moon occupied.

title: And Then There Were 10
description: Ben discovers the Omnitrix, and when it attaches itself to Ben's wrist, he discovers it allows him to become any one of ten alien heroes.

title: Together Forever
description: Connie has a really clear vision for her future. Steven wants to make sure he'll be a part of it.

title: Costume Crisis
description: Uncle Grandpa makes improvements to a kid's Halloween costume.

title: The More Things Change Part 1
description: Now on his own, Ben sets out to be a solo superhero, with new alien heroes at his disposal, but Grandpa Max has other plans. (Introducing Rook, Malware, Khyber, Nemetrix alien Crabdozer, new Ben aliens Feedback & Blox, Pakmar.)

title: Three Girls and a Monster/Monkey See, Doggy Two
description: Three Girls and a Monster: The girls are once again in a furious battle with a ferocious monster. But Blossom and Buttercup can't agree on how to fight the beast and Bubbles just wants everyone to get along./Monkey See, Doggy Two: Mojo has discovered a fatal flaw in his brilliant plan and decides to reenact it step-by-step. The girls think they're experiencing deja vu but it's really just Mojo working his maniacal mischief.

title: Snow Place Like Home
description: When the Bears realize whatever they build with snow comes to life they decide to build the biggest snow party of all time.

title: La Super Increible Aventura en Balsa
description: Unikitty y Hawkodile están "perdidos en el mar," varados en una balsa juntos. Hawkodile ve esto como una oportunidad para mostrarle a Unikitty que está preparado para cualquier cosa con sus habilidades de experto en supervivencia, pero para su sorpresa, todos sus planes fracasan, mientras que la tonta postura de Unikitty de "todo saldrá bien, vamos a divertirnos" está funcionando de una manera genial. ¿Será Hawkodile capaz de soltar su exceso de preparación para salvarlos a ambos, o acaso la diversión caprichosa de Unikitty será su perdición?

title: Mr. Universe
description: Greg takes Steven on the road to find the origins of the Universe name.

title: The Creeps
description: Finn and Jake receive an invitation to a masquerade dinner banquet from Count Creepystein.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Waterfilter
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max's trip to Niagara Falls is cut short by the horrid Hydromanders, creatures menacing them and their fellow tourists.

title: El Dragon Grief-Bringer
description: Nya y Kai, quienes se han convertido en los líderes de los Munces y Geckles, intentan unirlos para derrotar a su enemigo mutuo, el Hechicero Calavera.

title: Save Our Cinnamon
description: Granny's sister's beloved bakery, Cakery Bakery Dock, home of her wonderful trademark cinnamon rolls, is being put out of business so her landlord can tear down the bakery to build a parking lot. This galvanizes the Baby Looney Tunes to work together to bake one giant cinnamon roll as a tourist attraction to save the bakery, a project that ends up involving the whole town.

title: La Noche Brilla Especial: Capitulo 1
description: Cyborg queda atrapado en una realidad alternativa con un Dragón que quiere robarse una canción para sus propios fines malvados.

title: Scroogey Doo
description: The Scooby Gang enter Dickens' classic "A Christmas Carol" as they try to get to the bottom of the mysterious ghost tormenting Scrooge in 1843 England. Unfortunately, the Ghosts of Christmas Past, Present and Yet To Come begin to convince Velma she's on a disastrous path of her own.

title: The Big Sleep
description: When the Professor's latest invention wreaks havoc in the house, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls to stop it before it escapes.

title: The Cursed Cabinet of Professor Madds Markson!
description: When our mystery solving gang accepts the invitation to spend one night in the haunted Savannah Hotel in Las Vegas before its controlled demolition, they find that they're not alone. Famous magicians and entertainers Penn and Teller have also accepted the challenge. The winner gets a million bucks. While the loser may not make it out alive because the place is cursed and haunted by the ghost of infamous illusionist Professor Madds Markson and his horrible monster!

title: Halloween
description: In a strange town the gang tries to convince Fred he's mistaken in his firm belief that you can't solve a mystery on Halloween. When an evil witch appears and frightens the town into calling off Halloween, the gang learns this isn't Fred's first run-in with this witch and the true story behind Fred's feelings about Halloween.

title: Bakugan Battle Circus/Ebony Manor
description: Shun and Dan head to the Bakugan circus for a little fun, but the fun is interrupted when the star Bakugan are too exhausted to perform. Shun and Dan know the show must go on, and step in to lend a hand. Things go as planned until the evil Ringleader attempts to bring down the big top performance./ Lightning reunites with an old frenemy - Ebony. This time the kitty queen of the streets has a new home and is living a life of luxury with her new master.

title: Frybo
description: Steven helps a Boardie kid with his grueling job by using a magical gem shard that can bring clothing to life.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Los de Arriba Contra Atacan
description: Cole y los de abajo llegan para rescatar a los Ninjas. Para ello, Cole tendrá que recuperar las espadas legendarias, las Espadas de la Liberación.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: New Jersey
description: After donning a brand new Jersey, JP is recruited by the Hockey Kids! The only way to get JP back is for Craig and Kelsey to hit the ice!

title: Permanent Retirement
description: Grandpa, Gwen and Ben visit an old maid relative only to find that her retirement community has been overtaken by a shapeshifting aliens called Limax.

title: Night on Haunted Mountain
description: When Ethan and Gary are mountain climbing Mount Diabla out in the desert, they're attacked by Lilith, a dark-winged angel of destruction.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: A Jolt from the Past
description: Alien pests from Ben's youth come back, but now they need Ben's help. (Introducing Fistrick, & new Ben alien Gravattack.)

title: Lights! Camera! Tweety!
description: The Baby Looney Tunes are very eager to visit the local TV station, home of their favorite live children's show. When Floyd accidentally locks them inside the studio moments before airtime, they are forced to put on today's program all by themselves!

title: The Curse of Kaniaku
description: On a trip to Japan to visit Velma's friend, the gang comes face to face with the ancient crab monster Kaniaku. They attempt to solve a 700 year-old mystery; meanwhile Daphne accidentally becomes a viral media sensation in Japan.

title: Hashtag #1 Fan
description: Panda gets kidnapped by a pair of deranged French foxes.

title: Don't Press Play
description: The Titans must help De La Soul save their music after it is stolen by an alien.

title: Ranger Tabes
description: To recover a missing package, the Bears get help from Ranger Tabes, an eccentric forest ranger. But her overblown sense of justice might be too much for the Bears to handle.

title: Selva lunar
description: Stevonnie se encuentra solo en una aventura.

title: Bear Cleanse
description: A doctor tells the Bears to go on a cleanse to improve their health. But when Grizz realizes he can only eat what grizzly bears eat, he starts to lose his mind.

title: Temp Check
description: Rigby hires a temp to do his work but gets jealous when the temp becomes tight with Mordecai.

title: Vote Velma
description: When the ghost of a small town's founder returns to scare off mayoral candidates, the gang decides to run Velma as mayor to bait the ghost. They quickly discover however, that Velma lacks the skill set to make her a popular politician.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: The Gathering Gloom
description: When the gang is at Crystal Cove Cemetery watching a free screening of an old Vincent Van Ghoul movie with half the town, they are attacked by the Graveyard Ghoul!

title: Natural Gas
description: Outraged at the price they pay for water, gas, and electricity, the Titans go off the grid.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Bedlam in the Big Top
description: A ghost clown haunts a small circus, using hypnotism to bend locals to his will.

title: Benson Be Gone
description: Mordecai sees Pops naked and goes on a quest to unsee what he has seen.

title: Play Day
description: When the Looney Builders build themselves a playground, Daffy gets so excited about his section that he takes all the supplies for himself.

title: Nom Nom's Entourage
description: Nom Nom recruits the Bears to act as his entourage of friends. But when the Bears realize Nom Nom doesn't understand friendship, they decide to kick their day of bonding into high gear.

title: Bismuto Casual
description: Perla invita a Bismuto a la pista de patinaje para darle una lección sobre cómo forjar relaciones humanas.

title: El Hedor
description: El Sr. Small se vuelve salvaje cuando Gumball y Darwin exponen su hipocresía.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: El Lider Del Ring
description: Cuando Ben tiene una racha ganadora en un videojuego, se le ocurre una idea para ganar un partido real de lucha, hasta que un luchador intimidante decide convertirlo en un verdadero desafío.

title: The Filth
description: Ben is tasked with cleaning the Rust Bucket. But when he is tricked into letting the villainous and vile Fly Guys steal it, he must chase them down before they create an unstoppable maggot monster with sights firmly set on destroying Las Vegas.

title: Asteroid Blues
description: An asteroid is headed right for the kingdom, so Dr Fox leads the gang on a mission to save the kingdom by flying a rocket to the asteroid's surface and blowing it to bits with a huge bomb. But when they get there the gang finds the lonely asteroid is actually a super nice guy and don't want to blow him up.

title: Are We There Yet
description: During a long road trip, Floyd, obsessed with taking the Baby Looney Tunes to visit the distant, annual Acme Garlic Festival, endures countless variants of the universal kid question, are we there, yet? Despite Floyd's garlic agenda, fate has other plans.

title: Perricornio Patinador
description: Puppycorn quiere impresionar a sus amigos patinadores con sus habilidades fantásticas, el problema es que no tiene ninguna. Con la esperanza de aumentar su confianza, Unikitty y la pandilla se ponen los trajes invisibles de la Dra. Fox para ayudarlo secretamente a realizar movimientos imposibles. Pero hacen su trabajo demasiado bien y el "patinador profesional" Puppycorn está invitado a mostrar sus habilidades en una peligrosa competencia de escenas de riesgo. ¿Hasta dónde llegará la pandilla para ayudar al cachorro a realizar sus sueños inalcanzables e increíbles?

title: The Fastest Fast Food Fiend!
description: When Scooby and Shaggy compete in a fast food eating competition sponsored by the Doc Tally restaurant chain, they meet their ultimate challenge eating against none other than comedian Jim Gaffigan! And there's a horrible monster trying to stop the whole contest from finishing. Can Shaggy, Scooby and our mystery solving gang team up with Jim Gaffigan to save the fast food competition, and themselves?

title: Growing Pains
description: Steven visits a doctor for the first time.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Craig World
description: Craig creates an amusement park in the Creek! But when things start to get stale, he vows to make it bigger and better, no matter what it takes!

title: Gone to His Head
description: Uncle Grandpa's new found confidence makes his head big.

title: Dungeon Crawl!
description: Having joined forces with the Lowly in their quest to defeat King Vangelis, Cole, Wu, and Vania have to find a way out of the bottom of the mountain, a place said to be inescapable.

title: Riding the Storm Out
description: Ben and Gwen's camping trip is interrupted by the emotionless Weatherheads (Gust-o, Hail-o, & Shock-o) but a malfunctioning Omnitrix firing out a mishmash of aliens may not be the forecast for success.

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: BBRAEBDAY
description: Raven's demon side has the same birthday as Beast Boy, so the Titans go to Azarath to celebrate her Sinister Sixteen.

title: Porcentaje de Cerebro
description: Chico Bestia comienza a usar más del 10% de su cerebro en un esfuerzo por encontrar las imágenes ocultas en un rompecabezas.

title: Pony Tale
description: Uncle Grandpa grows a ponytail, which gains him the attention of a magical pony.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Log Cabin Fever
description: Granny takes the Baby Looney Tunes back to a simpler lifestyle during a rustic weekend spent in an 1800's log cabin, where they learn to enjoy life minus all modern conveniences. Baby Bugs and Baby Daffy get in trouble for smuggling their palm-sized computer game along, and they face Granny's consequences.

title: Zoo
description: Clarence and Belson make a true odd couple when they're paired up during a field trip to the zoo and find themselves locked inside after hours.

title: The Ascent
description: Cole, the Lowly, Princess Vania and Wu discover that the stone-mech is fueled by Elemental Power, and attach it to the mine-carts in an effort to blast their way out of the mountain to confront the evil Skull Sorcerer!

title: Sr. Universo
description: Greg lleva a Steven de viaje para encontrar los orígenes del nombre del Universo.

title: If It's Broke, Fix It
description: Dibble helps Grumpy work on his latest invention, a device to stop Bluster's bad vibe plow. Dibble's endless high spirits and sense of fun wear on Grumpy, until he finally says she can't work with him anymore. It's only later that Grumpy understands he needs Dibble's free-spirit inventiveness and creative energy.

title: On the Trail of the Cloud Bouncer
description: When spores from a strange plant take over control of the Cloudseeker, Cheer and the team must risk losing the vehicle - their home away from home and their only way back to Care-A-Lot - in order to save the Whiffles' newly-planted valley.

title: The Monster
description: Lumpy Space Princess's parents have come to ask Finn and Jake to find their daughter and convince her to come home.

title: The Treasure of Treetop Woods/Zee Makes an Amazing Maze!
description: Ranger Nat's hike turns to adventure when he finds a treasure map. The only problem is that he can't read it./Zee and MacBarm are setting up their corn maze with the help of Zee's Zee Mobile… that is, until it breaks down inside the maze.

title: A Dame-gerous Game
description: After Leshawna, Bridgette, Owen and Cody win a Hide & Seek competition, they're trapped on a private island by a jealous former champion and forced to play for their freedom.

title: Mother's Day
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais need to find the perfect Mother's Day gift. Will it be a cute card, a thoughtful painting or something entirely different? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Las Garras del Gato
description: Mientras disfruta de las vistas y los sonidos de un festival de música, Ben se eriza ante la sugerencia de Gwen de ser su nueva compañera, ya que el festival está amenazado por las ondas sonoras supersónicas de Lord Decibel.

title: Jump City Rock
description: The Titans team up with Nandi and Thomas Bushell to take down The Joker.

title: Web Weirdos
description: When Finn gets trapped in a giant spider web, he ends up playing marriage counselor to a couple of grumpy arachnids.

title: Inodoro Real
description: Cuando los otros chicos temen que Harold se haya descargado a sí mismo por accidente en el elegante inodoro nuevo de Chef, viajan al desagüe a rescatarlo. Pero, ¿encontrarán a Harold antes que el mítico Cocodrilo Rey los deje atrapados bajo tierra para siempre?

title: The Escape Room of Doom
description: The gang infiltrate an escape room game center to thwart Score Creeper, but their former foe claims he only works there to pay the bills.

title: Rio de Oro
description: Manzana y Cebolla intentan terminar un cuento antes de que el libro desaparezca para siempre.

title: Splash Zone
description: Mayor Foghorn Leghorn hires The Looney Builders to build a giant water slide for Looneyburg's waterpark. He keeps adding onto the design with the support of Bugs until problems arise.

title: Duele Crecer
description: Steven va al médico por primera vez.

title: La Grange Muralla
description: Ben, Gwen y el abuelo Max hacen un viaje a la Gran Muralla, pero su aventura por poco termina arruinada por los temerarios LaGrange y Vin Etanol, que intentan saltar sobre el monumento internacional. Ben debe subirse al Rustbuggy para ahuyentar a los enemigos.

title: Good Job
description: Falafel is starting to feel very underappreciated as the building's handyman. What's the point in all this back breaking work if not a single person will ever tell him, "Good Job"?

title: Hot Air Buffoon/Ploys R' Us
description: Hot Air Buffoon: The Mayor realizes the girls are doing all the work in his city for him. So he mans a hot air balloon and starts fighting crime the old-fashioned way./Ploys R' Us: The girls wake up to find their room filled with toys. They soon figure out that the Professor has been sleepwalking and stealing. Instead of reporting it, the girls take advantage of the situation.

title: Sigue Tus Suenos
description: Manzana y Cebollín necesitan encontrar un sueño que perseguir para que sus vidas tengan un rumbo.

title: Cat Fingers
description: Steven attempts to master the power of shape shifting, but can only shape shift his fingers into tiny cat heads.

title: Escapismo
description: Steven usa sus poderes psíquicos para conseguir ayuda.

title: One Hit Wonder
description: Apple & Onion can't bear to work another day in their dead end jobs at the dollar store but as always, money is the issue. If only there was a way they didn't have to worry about money any more.

title: Yip Yip, Book Book!/Stick to It!
description: It's the Pretty Big All City Read and Izzy and Barb are ready, that is, until all the books go missing!/Pretty Big City finds itself in a sticky situation when the factory starts spewing super sticky slime everywhere!

title: Jewel of the Aisle/Super Zeroes
description: Jewel of the Isle: A crook hides a huge diamond in a box of the girls' favorite cereal. But how can he trick the girls into giving him some cereal in order to get the jewel back?/Super Zeroes: The girls don't think they have enough superhero accessories like those found in the comic books. They begin to emulate their favorite characters, complete with gadgets and gizmos.

title: Jewel of the Aisle/Super Zeroes
description: Jewel of the Isle: A crook hides a huge diamond in a box of the girls' favorite cereal. But how can he trick the girls into giving him some cereal in order to get the jewel back?/Super Zeroes: The girls don't think they have enough superhero accessories like those found in the comic books. They begin to emulate their favorite characters, complete with gadgets and gizmos.

title: The Backstage Rage
description: A sinister puppet master manipulates the gang's investigation of a case of counterfeit.

title: Spooky Boo
description: After Clarence leads a few neighborhood kids through his homemade haunted house, Chelsea suggests they go to the high school kids haunted house for some real scares. When the gang makes a wrong turn they find themselves in a mysterious house on a hill full of creepy sounds, ghoulish shadows and mutant rat men!

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Welcome to Creek Street
description: Craig and his friends create their own neighborhood in the snow!

title: Foul Play in Funland
description: The gang investigates a haunted seaside amusement park.

title: The Slide
description: A chance encounter with the woman of his dreams inspires Rocky to stop living life online and find love with the help of the latest dating app. Gumball and Darwin try to help Rocky through the tricky world of online romance. In the race to find Rocky's dream girl, they discover people can forgive almost anything when you tell them you're acting in the name of love.

title: Grim Judgement
description: Hebediah Grim, a menacing Puritannical ancestor of Crystal Cove, terrorizes Lovers Lane.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: In Space
description: A very bad parking choice on Fred's part leads the gang to an asteroid mining base in outer space where an alien virus appears to be infecting the crew one by one, turning them into evil skull-headed aliens. The paranoid, terrified gang must try to solve the mystery before the virus reaches them.

title: Gettin' Twiggy with It/Cop Out
description: Getting' Twiggy with It: Mitch takes Twiggy, the class hamster, home for the weekend. But when Mitch flushes Twiggy down the toilet, he emerges bigger and badder than ever./Cop Out: A lazy Townsville cop gets fired and blames the girls for saving the day too often, thereby stealing his job. Now, it's payback time and he has the perfect plan to stop those pint-size punks.

title: A Matter of Pride
description: Apple & Onion's jobs have become too demeaning. They decide to put their foots down. It's a matter of pride.

title: This is My Jam
description: Rigby gets a terrible, terrible song stuck in his head and will go to any lengths to get it out.

title: El Recibo
description: Papá pierde un paquete y se ve envuelto en una pelea cada vez mayor con el repartidor.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Baba Yaga House
description: Squatter Otter tries to win Panda's trust and convince the Bears to live in a mysterious house.

title: Pelea Bot
description: La Dra. Fox se enorgullece de presentar su nueva máquina de combate definitiva y llevarla a un ring de combate científico subterráneo. Pero Hawkodile está celoso del bot de combate de la Dra. Fox, que supuestamente da mejores golpes que él, y declara que puede vencer a cualquier cosa que el bot pueda. Para demostrar su afirmación, se viste con piezas de robot de repuesto y entra en secreto en la batalla de robots. Con Unikitty como su entrenadora de lucha, ¿podrá Hawkodile sobrevivir al torneo, demostrar que es más fuerte que una máquina y salvarse del depósito de chatarra?

title: Hunted
description: Three alien bounty hunters are hot on Ben's trail. But one of them is a secret agent trying to make sure the Omnitrix does not fall into evil hands.

title: Welcome to the Unikingdom
description: After Unikitty finds out that tourism is down in the Unikingdom, she recruits the gang to make a tourism video to inspire people to visit the kingdom. But after calamities come one after another, Unikitty begins to think the video is going to turn out to be a disaster. However the friends save the day with some creativity and manage to get a single tourist to visit. Mission accomplished!

title: Beth and the Beanstalk
description: After having a chocolate bar confiscated by Chef, Beth finds herself in a parallel giant world and aims to get back her now giant chocolate bar.

title: El Camino en el Calabozo
description: En su misión de derrotar al Rey Vangelis, Cole, Wu y Vania unen fuerzas con "Los de abajo" para encontrar una forma de salir del fondo de la montaña.

title: El Dia de la Pinata
description: Izzy no logra golpear una piñata durante las celebraciones del Cinco de Mayo de la clase. Pero cuando esa piñata sin aplastar cobra vida y genera un ejército de piñatas malignas, es la hora de la verdad.

title: Salchichas y Dulce Golpe
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben superar sus obsesiones por las salchichas y los videojuegos.

title: Repulse!
description: Luthor infects Superman with a magnetic charge that repels everything. As the repulsing charge grows, the Magnetized Man of Steel is fated to spend the rest of his life isolated in space unless the Justice League can figure out a way to free him.

title: Grief Bringer
description: Nya and Kai, who have become the respective leaders of the Munce and Geckles, attempt to unite the tribes in an effort to defeat their mutual enemy, the Skull Sorcerer, who schemes against them.

title: Hiccup Havok
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a kid who can't get rid of the hiccups.

title: The Midnight Zone
description: When the DJ at the local radio station, K-GHOUL, is attacked, the gang investigates.

title: El Drama
description: Gumball intenta proteger a Darwin de Carrie, su inapropiada novia fantasma.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Grumpy Effect
description: Bluster traps Grumpy in a frustration-inducing labyrinth in an attempt to capture his grumpiness and turn it into the ultimate Bad Seed, which when planted will create new areas of Blusterland. The scheme backfires when Bluster refuses to listen to the warnings of his underlings, and Grumpy's inner kindness turns the Bad Seed into a force for good.

title: Pinata Regatta
description: Izzy can't bring herself to smash a Pinata during the class' Cinco De Mayo celebrations. But when that unsmashed Pinata comes to life and spawns an evil Pinata Army, it's batter up.

title: En Suenos
description: Los sueños de Steven comienzan a transmitirse en el televisor de su dormitorio.

title: Un Juego Peligroso
description: Después de que Leshawna, Bridgette, Owen y Cody ganan una competencia de jugar al escondite, están atrapados en una isla privada por una antigua campeona celosa y tienen que jugar a su juego.

title: Filtro Acuatico
description: El viaje de Ben, Gwen y Max a las Cataratas del Niágara se ve interrumpido por los horribles Hydromanders: unas criaturas que los amenazan a ellos y a los demás turistas.

title: Juntos por Siempre
description: Connie tiene una visión muy clara de su futuro, y Steven quiere asegurarse de ser parte de esa visión.

title: Beth y la Planta de Frijoles
description: Después de que Chef les confiscara una barra de chocolate, Beth se encuentra en un mundo paralelo gigante y quiere recuperar su barra que ahora es enorme.

title: But I Have a Receipt
description: When a bad game ruins game night, M & R attempt to return it to a not-so-pleasant store manager.

title: Sneeze
description: What is making Blippi sneeze? What makes anyone sneeze? Blippi shrinks down and flies up a nose to find out! A very mischievous piece of pollen demonstrates how to make a sneeze happen, resulting in Blippi himself getting blown away by a giant sneeze!

title: Speed Demon
description: Batman has to enlist the help of Jason Blood, aka the Demon, when Brother Blood turns the Batmobile into a sentient, demonic entity.

title: The Secret Life of Blossom Powerpuff
description: When Blossom can't join her favorite school club, she imagines what her life would be like if she joined other clubs.

title: Halt and Catch Silico
description: When a series of negative articles about the Powerpuff Girls are posted on the Internet, the girls track them back to Silico.

title: The Loophole
description: Gumball and Darwin give Bobert specific instructions to ensure he acts in a safe and responsible manner. When Bobert starts applying his robot logic to their rules, they soon realize they're going to have to be much clearer. Or he will end up destroying them all.

title: Agua de Ensalada Caliente
description: Robin debe salvar a los Estados Unidos de una nueva invasión británica cuando beber té vuelve ingleses a los demás Titanes.

title: Skiff Sails Sodor
description: When Skiff gets a crack in his hull, Thomas needs to move him overland to Harwick for repairs, but Skiff's land-sickness makes that challenging.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Total Eclipse of the Fart
description: After accidentally swallowing her first loose tooth and fearing that means no cash under the pillow, Leshawna tries to capture the tooth fairy. Instead, she accidentally captures the fart fairy. This comes with great consequence.

title: Bears in the Dark
description: The Bears search for their missing box in a dark and scary cave.

title: A Mid-Autumn Night's Scream
description: The Baby Looney Tunes first Halloween involves a costume contest for Lola, Melissa and Petunia, group trick-or-treating and Sylvester overcoming his fear of confronting an allegedly scary neighbor.

title: Things That Go Plunk
description: A shy, puny member of the Bad Crowd shows up at the Cloudseeker claiming he's been kicked out of Blusterland for being nice. The Bears, leery at first, take him in despite Grumpy's suspicions that he is in cahoots with Bluster. It appears Grumpy is right - but thanks to the Care Bears, the little guy turns into a good friend with the courage to thwart Bluster's latest scheme.

title: Together Breakfast
description: Steven tries to get the Gems to take part in his special breakfast tradition, but instead finds himself tumbling through the magical catacombs of the Crystal Gem's temple.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Cyber Luchadores
description: En Biggie Box Japón, Ben espera en una fila épica el lanzamiento de Cyber Luchadores, el último videojuego de Luchadores de Sumo. Pero muy pronto, Ben debe salvar la tienda: no de los clientes ansiosos por comprar el juego sino de Vapor Smythe, ique quiere modernizar un mecanismo gigantesco con sus vandálicos poderes de vapor!

title: Dusk Industries Under Attack/Taking Dan Back
description: Dusk Industries Under Attack: "Bad Dan" has his taken his rampage to Dusk Industries and this time he has help spreading the chaos and destruction, he's joined by Sophie, McQ, Everett, Storm and Haavik! The Awesome Brawlers are quickly on the scene try to bring an end to the show of destruction./ Taking Dan Back: "Bad Dan" with Haavik's crew and their fusion Bakugan continue the rampage at Dusk Industries. The Awesome Brawlers, with some help from Magnus, are determined to an end to this show of destruction and get their friend back!

title: Real Art
description: After Starfire buys an ugly painting, the Titans take her to the museum so she can experience real art.

title: Riffle the Whiffle
description: The Bears encounter a lost Whiffle whose only word is "Riffle." They have no idea who he is or where he came from. Dibble is tasked with looking out for him until they learn where he lives. At first delighted to have a new playmate, she grows frustrated when he seems only to want to get away. With the aid of the Bears, Dibble helps solve the mystery of who he is and where he belongs.

title: Asteroide Triste
description: Un asteroide viaja directo hacia el reino, por lo que la Dra. Fox se pone al frente de la banda en una misión para volar en un cohete hasta la superficie del asteroide y hacerlo explotar en pedazos con una enorme bomba para así salvar el reino. Pero al llegar, la banda descubre que el asteroide solitario es en realidad un tipo sumamente agradable y se rehúsan a hacerlo explotar. Por desgracia, el asteroide se entera del plan de Fox y sale corriendo llorando, icon la bomba aún en su interior! La Dra. Fox, arrepentida, lleva de urgencia a la banda tras el asteroide para levantarle el ánimo antes de que sea demasiado tarde.

title: Luthor in Paradise
description: With the aid of Circe the Witch, Luthor travels to Paradise Island to steal an artifact that will give him god-like powers. When Superman and Batman arrive on the island to bring him back, they find that they're almost as popular with the Amazons as Luthor on this woman-only island.

title: The Ring Leader
description: While winning big on a Sumo Slammers video game, Ben gets the idea to win a wrestling match for real until an intimidating wrestler named Iron Kyle decides to make it a true challenge.

title: Royal Flush
description: When the other kids fear Harold has accidentally flushed himself down Chef's fancy new toilet, they travel into the sewer on a rescue mission. But will they find Harold before the mythical Alligator King traps them underground forever?

title: Nothing Can Stop Us
description: Hot Dog has the audition of his life but he is missing something crucial. Apple and Onion are tasked with bringing it to him and they are adamant that nothing will stand in their way.

title: Bismuth Casual
description: Pearl invites Bismuth to the roller rink for a lesson on how to forge human relationships.

title: The Darkest Hour
description: Forced to flee by the arrival of Grief-Bringer, the ninja, the Munce and the Geckles take refuge in the Geckle Strong-Cave. But the bitter feud between Munce and Geckles threatens to tear them apart, just when unity is needed most…when they are about to confront the Skull Sorcerer and Grief-Bringer!

title: Play Date
description: Toyman takes over the Justice League and turns them into avatars in a diabolical video game.

title: Golden Bakugan Encounter/Ties of Gold
description: Golden Bakugan Encounter: Dan and Shun, split up from the rest of Awesome Brawlers, are traveling in through the maze when they discover McQ. It turns out McQ is seeking a golden Bakugan. When the boys go in for a closer look, they are startled by an old friend, and together confront McQ./Ties of Gold: The now reunited Awesome Brawlers are once again confronted by Storm, McQ, Sophie and Everett, who are on the hunt for golden Bakugan. With tired Bakugan, the Awesome Brawlers will have to give it their all to defend against this evil.

title: El Hada de los Gases
description: Después de perder su primer diente flojo por accidente y temer el no tener efectivo bajo la almohada, Leshawna intenta capturar al hada de los dientes. En vez de eso, captura al hada de los gases. Esto trae grandes consecuencias.

title: Juntos Solos
description: Steven organiza una fiesta para reunir a su familia.

title: It Came From the Nightosphere
description: Against Marceline's wishes, Finn conjures her father, the Lord of Evil, and attempts to reconcile their rocky relationship. But when the Lord of Evil discovers his daughter has turned the family axe into a bass guitar, he takes it from her and starts sucking up all the souls in Ooo! Finn must find a way to stop the Lord of Evil and get Marceline's guitar back.

title: El Ascenso
description: Cole, los de abajo, la princesa Vania y Wu salen de la montaña para enfrentarse al malvado Hechicero Calavera.

title: Capsula del tiempo
description: La banda pone sus objetos favoritos dentro de una capsula del tiempo para enviarlas 100 años al futuro, pero quedan atrapados dentro antes de que la puerta se cierre.

title: Muscle Woman
description: Mordecai & Rigby attempt to get Muscle Man and his girlfriend back together, until she begins to fall for Mordecai.

title: Fan or Foe
description: When Elder Con comes to the Creek, Craig, Kelsey and JP each have a con experience they'll never forget.

title: Night Terrors
description: When a visiting family finds some terrifying specters in an old library high in the hills above Crystal Cove, the gang investigates.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Clocktopus
description: In a peaceful coastal town, Ben must not only face the archaic antagonist Steam Smythe and his latest creation, the Clocktopus, but also his deepest, darkest fear: Squids!

title: Washington B.C.
description: Ben must use the Omnitrix to transform into alien heroes to battle Dr. Amino and his transmorphed dinosaurs running rampant in Washington DC.

title: Afraid of the Dark
description: When UG helps a little girl who is afraid of the dark, he convinces her there's nothing to be afraid of but their imaginations.  But when their imaginations prove to be pretty terrifying, they go on a quest to turn on the lights.

title: Scary Tales
description: During the gang's Halloween party, Unikitty discovers Brick isn't scared of anything! To get him in the holiday spirit, the gang tell their own ideas of what a spooky story is, hoping to scare the emotionless Rick for once, with each tale even scarier (and sillier) than the last!

title: Puddle Eyes
description: A nap in mud seals Clarence's eyes and leaves him sightless, potentially dooming his team's chances in the school's ill-conceived "Vision Bee."

title: When Urkel-Bots Go Bad!
description: When Steve Urkel enlists the help of our mystery solving gang to track down the rampaging Urkel-Bot, they stumble onto a deeper mystery. It seems the Urkel-Bot has gone haywire and escaped a Chicago Museum! The mystery deepens with the appearance of a Technomancer, controlling all the robots! Can our gang and Urkel survive an onslaught of the Technomancer's angry robots? And, more importantly, can our gang survive Urkel?

title: Nightmare/Bad Dan
description: Nightmare: Dan hasn't been sleeping well lately. No "sleep brawling" this time, but he's constantly tossing and turning. It turns out, Dan's dreams have been hijacked by Haavik, who's trying to spread his vision of chaos and destruction to Dan!/Bad Dan: Haavik has taken control of Dan and sends him on a Bakugan rampage! With "Bad Dan" causing all kinds of havoc and destruction, the rest of the Awesome Brawlers have no choice but to roll out to try to contain "Bad Dan".

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Sillon
description: Unikitty encuentra una vieja silla reclinable en la acera, pero ve su belleza interior y lo lleva a casa para mostrárselo a la pandilla. En una serie de situaciones absurdas y divertidas, descubrimos cómo una silla sucia e inanimada entra en cada una de sus vidas y las cambia para mejor. Pronto aprendemos que la querida y dulce silla era demasiado buena para este mundo.

title: A New View for Thomas
description: When Thomas spends the day carrying rockstar idol Harold across Sodor, he gains a new perspective on just how amazing it is to be his engine-self.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Blaze
description: Los Titanes se convierten en hackers para detener a una pandilla de piratas informáticos.

title: Trouble Helix
description: Flashback episode: Young Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max visit Azmuth on Galvan Prime. There, they have their first encounter with Malware, a corrupted Mechamorph who's determined to make Azmuth cure him, by any means!

title: La Amiga
description: Anaís y Jamie forjan una extraña amistad cuando se las acusa de un crimen que no cometieron.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Baa Baa Black Sheep
description: It's getting chilly on the farm! Summers dwindled into autumn and everyone is in need of some winter clothing

title: Sabro Atraco
description: Richard preparó uno de los postres más sabrosos de todos los tiempos, pero lo cerró con llave hasta que los amigos terminen su cena aburrida. Esto no va a seguir así. Para organizar un atraco, Unikitty organiza a sus amigos como un comité de expertos para entrar, salir y comer ese sabroso bocadillo sin que Richard lo sepa. Pero este atraco tiene un traspié. ¿Podrán los amigos llevarse el pastel?

title: Rooms
description: The Bears switch bedrooms for the night and get a glimpse of the living space of one of their brothers. But the deeper they go, hidden secrets are revealed.

title: The Code
description: Gumball learns the Wattersons have been stealing Mr. Robinson's wi-fi for years. When it goes down, they try and live without it but life offline proves too hard. Gumball and Darwin decide to hack their way through cyberspace to learn Mr Robinson's passcode.

title: The Scam
description: At Halloween show and tell, the class isn't buying Gumball's story about Gargaroth the Devourer until Carrie fakes a terrifying haunting. The kids convince the school to hire them as ghost exterminators and take their payment in Halloween candy. But when it turns out Gargaroth is real, suddenly Gumball is expected to be the town's savior.

title: Losing Ice
description: Feeling unappreciated, Ice Bear leaves his brothers to be the chef of a restaurant. Desperate to fill the void, Grizz and Panda look for Ice Bear's replacement.

title: Ego - Egoista
description: Manzana y Cebolla tienen que demostrar que no son egoístas cuando hacen sus buenas acciones.

title: Charlas Nocturnas
description: La luna está aburrida de tomar el turno de noche, ya que todos siempre están dormidos. Entonces, Unikitty lidera a la pandilla en la presentación de un programa de entrevistas nocturno exagerado para mantener la luna ocupada.

title: MacGuffin
description: Uncle Grandpa and a kid embark on a dangerous jungle adventure in search of a legendary MacGuffin.

title: The Test
description: Gumball is livid when an online test keeps telling him that his character-type is "The Loser". He's convinced the only way to shake off this label is to do the opposite of everything he normally would. But Gumball suppressing his natural instincts leaves a vacuum, a Gumball-shaped hole that someone has to fill. That someone is Tobias, who starts turning the whole show into a cliched sitcom.

title: Spiderweb
description: A gorgeous spider web in the park has Blippi wondering "How do spiders make their webs?" He sets off to find the answer! A very talented spider explains the artistic process and Blippi is surprised by the masterful picture that ends up in the spiders' web!

title: Cheeseburger Backpack
description: A mission to the Lunar Sea Spire takes a treacherous turn, but Steven has packed his totally amazing Cheeseburger Backpack with anything they could ever need!

title: Time Capsule
description: The gang puts their favorite items in a Time Capsule to send 100 years in the future, but they get stuck inside right before the door seals. Dr Fox tries to convince the gang to let her use their favorite items to escape the capsule, and each character tells a story about why their favorite item is their favorite, and why Dr Fox can't destroy it to escape. Finally it's revealed that Unikitty's favorite thing was friendship and she trapped everyone in the capsule on purpose, so the future could see their friendship! Unfortunately for the gang, even after they surrender their favorite items to escape, it doesn't work and they have to wait 100 years to finally leave the capsule.

title: Big Ben 10
description: Cuando Ben y su familia viajan a Londres para visitar el legendario Big Ben, los hermanos Bicho están allí para darles la bienvenida, obviamente con un nuevo plan escandalosamente exagerado: iencoger la campana del Big Ben para robarla!

title: Bienvenidos al Unireino
description: Después de descubrir que el turismo escasea en el Unireino, Unikitty recluta a la banda para que hagan un video que inspire a la gente a visitar el reino. Pero luego de varias calamidades, Unikitty comienza a creer que el video resultará siendo un desastre. Sin embargo, los amigos salvan el día con algo de creatividad y logran hacer que un solo turista los visite. iMisión cumplida!

title: Spoooooky Game
description: The gang's weekly board game night has been getting a little too competitive lately, so when Unikitty finds a spooky old board game that's clearly haunted, their desire to win gets turned upside down, but cursed or not, they'll be the first to the finish line!

title: Sobreviviendo A La Tormenta
description: El campamento de Ben y Gwen se ve interrumpido por los gélidos Weatherheads -Gust-o, Hail-o, & Shock-o-, pero un Omnitrix que funciona mal y dispara un montón de extraterrestres podría no ser un pronóstico de éxito.

title: Ancestor Act
description: When Gumball's sister Anais researches the Watterson family tree, she uncovers a long history of nonsense. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Boogie Frights/Abracadaver
description: Boogie Frights: The Boogie Man creates perpetual night by launching a huge disco ball to block out the sun. While evil creatures are dancing and destroying in the dark, the Powerpuff Girls plot to crash the ball./Abracadaver: Al Lusion, the old-time Townsville magician, pulls off his greatest stunt yet when he comes back from the dead as the zombie Abracadaver to haunt Townsville.

title: Halloween En El Arroyo
description: Llegó Halloween al bosque, y Craig se embarca en una misión para recolectar la mayor cantidad de dulces como sea humanamente posible. Pero un espíritu aterrador del pasado del bosque amenaza su botín.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Hat Trick
description: When Felix Faust steals Zatanna's magical top hat, the Justice League must help retrieve it before the evil wizard can use it to create a magic portal, releasing the demon Ghast.
